          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2100 ofd: tune batched precreate down",
        "message": "LU-2100 ofd: tune batched precreate down\n\ndepending on load OFD may try to precreate many objects\nwithin a single transasction (up to 128). on a small\nsystem this may lead to transaction overflow, complains\nfrom OSD. to prevent this OSD may return -ENOSPC from\ndt_trans_start() and OFD can decrease number of batched\ncreates.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Idbac6149e75a7c1d8552d0601de5faabe0743154\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
